subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Rashad Greene returned a punt 63 yards, setting up a 5-yard touchdown pass from Blake Bortles to Julius Thomas with 3 minutes 30 seconds remaining, and Jacksonville beat visiting Tennessee, 19-13.
